GameElements

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • GameElements.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Consumable, Player, Projectile, Tile

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents every object in our game, for example a player or an item. It provides methods and fields that all objects in our game share.
    Version:
    5/17/19
    Author:
    Leofeng, Roee, Sky
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
